column5: Got this picture sent to me a couple of hours ago. It is a giant Alaskan Middle Kenai bow caught last week by a friends buddy. These guys are the reason I head there every September. Just 8 1/2 days to go.
You could feed all of OFC with that,well, thats if TJ dosent show up.  Thats huge Dave.
That Rainbow is incredible. Native and natural can't be beat.
That thing looks like a triploid!!!!!  What an absolute beast!
I guess that's what a steady diet of salmon eggs will do for you! Beauty fish.
